project_descr: The project responds to immediate needs of the Ukrainian government and wider society in addressing some of the drivers of political instability, human rights violations and social discontent across the country, and conflict in the Donbas region.

outputs.output_descr: Processes of reforming key areas of governance and supporting recovery are better coordinated in government, rights-based and more representative of popular aspirations.

project_title: governance and recovery rapid intervention project
